@startuml
title 미핏 - 회원가입 → 이메일 인증 → JWT → 프로필 완성 시퀀스

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  ActorBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantBorderColor #2196F3
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantFontSize 11
  BoxBorderColor #B0BEC5
  BoxBackgroundColor #ECEFF1
}

actor "사용자" as U
participant "Frontend\n(useAuthStore)" as FE
participant "Backend\n(Django + DRF)" as BE
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "Redis\n(broker)" as Q
participant "Celery Worker" as W
participant "SMTP" as SMTP

== Step 1. 회원가입 (FR-AUTH-01) ==

U -> FE : 이메일 / 비밀번호 / 이름 입력
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/users/sign-up/
activate BE
  BE -> BE : SignUpService.execute()
  BE -> DB : User 생성 (email_confirmed_at=null,\n  profile_completed_at=null)
  BE -> DB : GrantInitialSubscriptionTicketsService\n(FREE 플랜 정책 기준 daily_count 초기화)
  BE -> Q : on_commit: dispatch\nRegisteredSendVerificationEmailTask
  BE -> BE : RefreshToken.for_user(user)\n(rest_framework_simplejwt)
  BE --> FE : { access, refresh } + user 메타
deactivate BE
FE -> FE : setTokens(access)
FE -> BE : GET /api/v1/users/me/ (Bearer)
BE --> FE : { isEmailConfirmed: false,\n  isProfileCompleted: false }
FE -> FE : navigate("/verify-email")

== Step 2. 인증 코드 비동기 발송 (FR-AUTH-02, FR-AUTH-04) ==

Q -> W : pull RegisteredSendVerificationEmailTask
activate W
  W -> W : SendVerificationEmailService.execute()
  W -> W : 6 자리 코드 생성 (대문자 + 숫자)
  W -> DB : EmailVerificationCode 저장\n(expires_at = now + 10분, used_at=null)
  W -> SMTP : send_mail("verification_code.html", { code })
deactivate W
SMTP --> U : 인증 메일 수신

== Step 3. 코드 입력 + 검증 (FR-AUTH-05) ==

U -> FE : 6 자리 코드 입력
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/users/verify-email/ (Bearer)\n{ code }
activate BE
  BE -> BE : VerifyEmailService.execute()
  BE -> DB : EmailVerificationCode.active(user)\n  .get(code=code)
  note right of DB
    .active() = user 일치
    + used_at IS NULL
    + expires_at > now()
  end note

  alt 만료 / 사용된 코드 / 오타
    BE --> FE : 400 ValidationException\n("invalid_code" / "expired")
  else 유효
    BE -> DB : code_obj.used_at = now\nuser.email_confirmed_at = now
    BE --> FE : 200 OK
  end
deactivate BE

FE -> BE : GET /api/v1/users/me/
BE --> FE : { isEmailConfirmed: true,\n  isProfileCompleted: false }
FE -> FE : navigate("/onboarding")

== Step 4. 프로필 완성 (FR-AUTH-10) ==

U -> FE : 직무 카테고리 / 직무 / 경력 단계 선택
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/profiles/me/\n{ job_category, jobs[], career_level }
activate BE
  BE -> DB : Profile 업데이트\nuser.profile_completed_at = now
  BE --> FE : 200 OK
deactivate BE
FE -> FE : navigate("/")\n(홈 + 모든 도메인 접근 가능)

== Step 5. 로그인 / 토큰 갱신 (FR-AUTH-04, FR-AUTH-07) ==

U -> FE : 재로그인
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/users/sign-in/\n{ email, password }
activate BE
  BE -> BE : SignInService.execute()
  BE -> BE : authenticate(email, password)
  BE -> BE : RefreshToken.for_user(user)
  BE --> FE : { access, refresh }
deactivate BE

note over FE, BE
  access 만료 시:
  POST /api/v1/users/token/refresh/
  → 새 access 발급 (refresh 검증)
end note

== Step 6. 비밀번호 재설정 (FR-AUTH-08) ==

U -> FE : "비밀번호 찾기" → 이메일 입력
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/users/password-reset/
activate BE
  BE -> BE : RequestPasswordResetService.execute()
  BE -> DB : 기존 활성 PasswordResetToken 무효화
  BE -> DB : 새 PasswordResetToken(token=UUID, expires_at=now+30분)
  BE -> Q : dispatch RegisteredSendPasswordResetEmailTask
  BE --> FE : 200 OK
deactivate BE
Q -> W : pull task
W -> SMTP : send_mail("password_reset.html", { reset_link })
SMTP --> U : 재설정 링크 메일

U -> FE : 링크 클릭 → /reset-password?token={uuid}
U -> FE : 새 비밀번호 입력
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/users/password-reset/confirm/
activate BE
  BE -> BE : ConfirmPasswordResetService.execute()
  BE -> DB : PasswordResetToken 조회
  alt 사용됨 / 만료됨
    BE --> FE : 400 ValidationException
  else 유효
    BE -> DB : user.set_password(new_pw)\ntoken.used_at = now
    BE --> FE : 200 OK
  end
deactivate BE

footer MeFit - 인증 + 온보딩 (FR-AUTH-01~10) — JWT + Celery 비동기 메일
@enduml
